A vintage 1970s technical illustration style image depicting a stream of glowing amber documents flowing from an ornate wooden filing cabinet with brass handles, transforming mid-air into sleek blue geometric data cubes as they arc gracefully toward a floating cloud-shaped repository made of interconnected hexagonal nodes. The scene is set against a warm sepia-toned background with subtle grid lines reminiscent of old engineering blueprints. The documents shed their paper texture like autumn leaves as they metamorphose, creating a visual bridge between analog and digital storage. Warm orange and cool teal color palette with aged paper texture overlay.
